data.description: Discover the epitome of serene living in this exquisite all-brick ranch home nestled in the picturesque Herrington Hills division. With a walkout basement that extends the living space, you'll find tranquility and luxury combined.Relish breathtaking views of rolling hills and graceful deer from your own private back deck, creating an idyllic backdrop for outdoor gatherings or peaceful moments of reflection. This property is a paradise for nature enthusiasts.For water lovers, Herrington Hills offers a private boat dock granting access to the pristine waters of Lake Herrington, perfect for boating and fishing adventures. Additionally, the subdivision provides secure boat and RV storage facilities, ensuring your prized possessions are well-protected.Experience the best of Kentucky's natural beauty and recreational amenities while enjoying the comfort and elegance of this charming ranch home. Being sold AS-IS
